{"tid":325004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國開始量産彩虹5軍用無人機     航程超1萬公里","createTime":"2017-07-17T01:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:39:16.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3107fbad541c50b46005f41ed8de100ff0ceea","tid":325004,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"　　<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/093838_8bef3adba494dcd79ea8ab8f491e207d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F093838_8bef3adba494dcd79ea8ab8f491e207d.jpg&h=99a69b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/093840_d9757b869ed67d75ff017d72ad6418d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F093840_d9757b869ed67d75ff017d72ad6418d5.jpg&h=92a22c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/093841_ec18c65cd64c329711f8a87cebc4ce1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F093841_ec18c65cd64c329711f8a87cebc4ce1b.jpg&h=6a41ac3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國自主研發的中高端大型「察打一體」無人機「彩虹―5」7月15日正式進入批量生産階段。專家介紹，飛機還將進行多次試驗飛行，並根據用戶不同需求進行微調。<br />\n<br />\n　　「彩虹―5」是由中國航天科技集團公司十一院研製的一款大型中空長航時無人機，翼展21米，最大起飛重量達3300千克，最大航程超過10000千米。該型飛機主要用於實施全天時偵察監視、巡邏、目標精確定位、打擊毀傷效果評估等任務。"},{"pid":"0c9374bd0f59a331c9e156feb138cd63d3467a7f","tid":325004,"uid":46644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9202cde4581bfbebb0e12255dbbf3f0a84c783a1","tid":325004,"uid":46644,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ae4cc11cf65431a5ac0cbcd821308ebc1a6d3c4","tid":325004,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\"